snippet.title: Phantom: Covert Ops  |  Gameplay Walkthrough  |  Oculus Quest + Rift Platform
snippet.description:
Join nDreams Game Director Lewis Brundish for a walk through some gameplay of Phantom: Covert Ops!

In this upcoming title that redefines the stealth genre, you play as an elite operative deep in enemy waters. Can you navigate your kayak to victory?
